Once on each of your turns, you can jump up to [1] by spending only [2] of movement.

At Warlock Level 5, it will upgrade to Ascendant Step.
Once on each of your turns, you can Jump up to [1] long and [2] high by spending only [3] of movement.
Once on each of your turns, you can Levitate up to [1] long and [2] high by spending only [3] of movement.

You gain <LSTag Tooltip="MusicalInstrumentProficiency">Musical Instrument Proficiency</LSTag>, and can <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="CL_Shout_Doot">magically summon an instrument of your choice</LSTag>.
